• Created the first GUI application in MATLAB for deep brain stimulation research, reducing data collection time by over 50% and minimizing interoperability errors from over 5 minutes to 10-60 milliseconds. https://github.com/mobatusi/NXSD_GUI.

  • Managed the transfer of over 20 TB of research data from local servers to the distributed database CranialVault Cloud (CranialCloud)..
